      "content": "i mean yeah i'll drink water but i'm kinda in the middle of a big project and i really dont want to waste hours at the clinic if it's just stress or something. do u think it could just be a tension headache or maybe just too much caffeine? i feel like if i just take some ibuprofen and get some sleep i'll be fine by tomorrow right?",
